{
  "texts": [
    "The short and long feature sets achieved an AUROC of 0.80 and 0.82 on the preprocessing test subset respectively.",
    "The final features for each set are shown in. 3.",
    "Finally, alternative cutoff thresholds were explored for both models to maximise the AUROC and minimise the FPR (Supplementary Fig. 2).",
    "This then allows for a traffic light system to be employed at deployment for simplicity and interpretability (Fig. 4).",
    "Youden's index 27 which optimises the AUROC, found the 1st cutoff point of 0.54 and 0.52 for the short and long models respectively."
  ]
}